endDate.description:
Only transactions before the End Date will be returned.
Note: The maximum date range is one year. Valid ISO-8601 formats are :
yyyy-MM-dd.

startDate.description:
Only transactions after the Start Date will be returned.
Note: The maximum date range is one year. Valid ISO-8601 formats are :
yyyy-MM-dd.

symbol.description: Only transactions with the specified symbol will be returned.

type.description: Only transactions with the specified type will be returned.
